race.comment: VERBIL (5) talented gelding with a good record over this course and distance. Forced to work hard from the wide gate and the early effort told late with the 60kg when a tiring fourth over 1550m at this track. Gets the right set-up for this and has a distinct fitness edge over the bulk of these. BRAVISSIMA (9) underrated Goulburn-trained mare looking for the 1550m now. Twenty-eight days between runs when she gripped on late for a courageous fifth over 1400m at Rosehill in stronger company. Holds a forward position and can take this out. BAT OUT OF HELL (6) handy gelding who was strong through the line over the unsuitable trip first-up when fifth over 1250m here. Adept in all conditions and sure to be thereabouts. FORECASTER (8) consistent gelding who looks up to this stronger contest after scoring a convincing victory over this track and trip. Will go forward again and take a hand in the finish.
